(377, 1, '2013-11-01 23:02:52', '2013-11-01 23:02:52', '[row snaps="tlr0"][column size="12" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [slider ]294[/slider][/column][/row][row snaps="0lr0"][column size="10" offset="1" content_align="center" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<h1 style="text-align: center;">Welcome to Essenza&#39;s corporate demo</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The reason that we created this demo is to show you what other possibilities Essenza has besides the default grid, gallery and blog modules. Essenza really is a premium theme with additional fullscreen grid and gallery options, instead of a grid based theme with some simple page options!&nbsp;<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; word-spacing: 0em;">Based on all the feedback and suggestions we got during the first two weeks online, we decided to drastically change the &#39;regular&#39; page admin options, giving full freedom for creativity to the user!</span></p>[/text][vertical_space ]20[/vertical_space][divider width="30" thickness="1" line_style="solid" line_color="#e1e1e1" margin_top="0" margin_bottom="10" ][/divider][text ]<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 107, 69); font-family: ''Open Sans''; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px; text-align: center;">A few highlights about what has changed:</span></p>[/text][/column][/row][row snaps="000b"][column size="5" offset="1" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<h4 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:48px;"><span style="color:#776B5F;">[i]fa-fullscreen[/i]</span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">Perfect page alignment options</span></h5>\r\n\r\n<p style="word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">Where V1 only enabled to align a fixed 770 pixels wide page to align left, centered and right, V2 gives you complete control over alignment, width and margins. This enables you to create beautiful pages like this one.</p>[/text][vertical_space ]30[/vertical_space][/column][column size="5" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<h4 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:48px;"><span style="color:#776B5F;">[i]fa-outdent[/i]</span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">Content to side snapping</span></h5>\r\n\r\n<p style="word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">In V2 it is possible to &#39;snap&#39; content to the sides of a page. An example is the slider here in top, snapping to the left, top and right side of the page. It also allows you to create pages like the <a href="replace_with_urlsliders" target="_self">stacked slider homepage</a>.</p>[/text][vertical_space ]30[/vertical_space][/column][/row][row snaps="000b"][column size="5" offset="1" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<h4 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 48px;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 107, 95);">[i]fa-download[/i]</span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">Save and load pages</span></h5>\r\n\r\n<p style="word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">With new pagebuilder options, creating custom pages like this one becomes more attractive. To make it extra easy to create multiple pages with the same layout, in V2 it is possible to save a page layout and load that layout in any other page!</p>[/text][vertical_space ]30[/vertical_space][/column][column size="5" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<h4 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 48px;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 107, 95);">[i]fa-code[/i]</span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">New and improved shortcodes</span></h5>\r\n\r\n<p style="word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">V2 provides you with some cool new shortcodes to play with like &#39;Image Button&#39; and &#39;Text Header&#39;. Also, the text editors in the pagebuilder give more freedom on how to use fonts. Last but not least, some improvements to existing shortcodes have been made!</p>[/text][/column][/row][row snaps="0000"][column size="5" offset="1" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [/column][column size="5" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [/column][/row][row snaps="0lr0"][column size="12" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [divider width="100" thickness="1" line_style="solid" line_color="#e1e1e1" margin_top="0" margin_bottom="10" ][/divider][/column][/row][row snaps="0000"][column size="3" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="true" padding="0px 20px 0px 20px"] [text ]<h5>About us</h5>[/text][vertical_space ][/vertical_space][text ]<p>Fruitcake sweet roll powder wafer croissant dessert liquorice. Lollipop halvah chupa chups tart sesame snaps caramels cookie apple pie muffin. Cookie dessert sugar plum donut jelly beans chocolate. Sweet roll drag&eacute;e sweet roll cotton candy cotton candy lemon drops brownie topping lollipop.</p>[/text][vertical_space ]10[/vertical_space][/column][column size="3" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="true" padding="0px 20px 0px 20px"] [text ]<h5>Latest posts</h5>[/text][display-posts posts_per_page="3" orderby="date" order="DESC" offset="0" ][/display-posts][vertical_space ]10[/vertical_space][/column][column size="3" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="true" padding="0px 20px 0px 20px"] [text ]<h5>On Dribbble</h5