ht, V2 gives you complete control over alignment, width and margins. This enables you to create beautiful pages like this one.</p>[/text][vertical_space ]30[/vertical_space][/column][column size="5" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<h4 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:48px;"><span style="color:#776B5F;">[i]fa-outdent[/i]</span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">Content to side snapping</span></h5>\r\n\r\n<p style="word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">In V2 it is possible to &#39;snap&#39; content to the sides of a page. An example is the slider here in top, snapping to the left, top and right side of the page. It also allows you to create pages like the <a href="replace_with_urlsliders" target="_self">stacked slider homepage</a>.</p>[/text][vertical_space ]30[/vertical_space][/column][/row][row snaps="000b"][column size="5" offset="1" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<h4 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 48px;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 107, 95);">[i]fa-download[/i]</span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">Save and load pages</span></h5>\r\n\r\n<p style="word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">With new pagebuilder options, creating custom pages like this one becomes more attractive. To make it extra easy to create multiple pages with the same layout, in V2 it is possible to save a page layout and load that layout in any other page!</p>[/text][vertical_space ]30[/vertical_space][/column][column size="5" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<h4 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 48px;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 107, 95);">[i]fa-code[/i]</span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">New and improved shortcodes</span></h5>\r\n\r\n<p style="word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">V2 provides you with some cool new shortcodes to play with like &#39;Image Button&#39; and &#39;Text Header&#39;. Also, the text editors in the pagebuilder give more freedom on how to use fonts. Last but not least, some improvements to existing shortcodes have been made!</p>[/text][vertical_space ]30[/vertical_space][/column][/row][row snaps="0000"][column size="5" offset="1" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<h4 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 48px;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 107, 95);">[i]fa-sort-amount-asc[/i]</span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">Seperated submenus</h5>\r\n\r\n<p style="word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">Of course it was already possible to have submenus in V1, but the only option was having a fullwidth submenu bar as in the <a href="replace_with_url" target="_blank">creative demo</a>. In V2 it is possible to have seperated submenus with lots of styling options to create the exact look you want!</p>[/text][vertical_space ]30[/vertical_space][/column][column size="5" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<h4 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 48px;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 107, 95);">[i]fa-bug[/i]</span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">Bug fixes and IE compatibility</h5>\r\n\r\n<p style="word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;">What would an update be without fixing bugs?! We solved various problems like pages not showing in Internet Explorer, homepages having longer permalinks, the website returning to home after refreshing and more. Found something new? Let us know and we&#39;ll fix it asap!</p>[/text][vertical_space ]30[/vertical_space][/column][/row][row snaps="0lr0"][column size="12" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [actionbox title="Wow, that sounds amazing! Where can I buy Essenza?" title_float="left" title_margin="30px" title_color="#e96b45" text="" text_float="left" text_margin="0px" text_color="#ffffff" button_float="none" button_margin="0" background_color="#13100e" border_width="0" border_style="solid" border_color="#242424" vertical_padding="20" horizontal_padding="20" ]{"field0":"20","field1":"10","field2":"0","field3":"0","field4":"#fa5654","field5":"#222222","field6":"#fa5654","field7":"#222222","field8":"100","field9":"100","field10":"Open_Sans:300","field11":"13","field12":"#ffffff","field13":"#ffffff","field14":"0.2","field15":"ease-out","field16":"Button [i]icon-double-angle-right[/i]","field17":"center","field18":"#","field19":""}[/actionbox][/column][/row][row snaps="0lr0"][column size="12" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [divider width="100" thickness="1" line_style="solid" line_color="#e1e1e1" margin_top="0" margin_bottom="10" ][/divider][/column][/row][row snaps="0000"][column size="3" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="true" padding="0px 20px 0px 20px"] [text ]<h5>About us</h5>[/text][vertical_space ][/vertical_space][text ]<p>Fruitcake sweet roll powder wafer croissant dessert liquorice. Lollipop halvah chupa chups tart sesame snaps caramels cookie apple pie muffin. Cookie dessert sugar plum donut jelly beans chocolate. Sweet roll drag&eacute;e sweet roll cotton candy cotton candy lemon drops brownie topping lollipop.</p>[/text][vertical_space ]10[/vertical_space][/column][column size="3" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="true" padding="0px 20px 0px 20px"] [text ]<h5>Latest posts</h5>[/text][display-posts posts_per_page="3" orderby="date" order="DESC" offset="0" ][/display-posts][vertical_space ]10[/vertical_space][/column][column size="3" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="true" padding="0px 20px 0px 20px"] [text ]<h5>On Dribbble</h5>[/text][vertical_space ]12[/vertical_space][dribbble number="11" width="90" height="90" ]99miles[/dribbble][vertical_space ]10[/vertical_space][/column][column size="3" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="true" padding="0px 20px 0px 20px"] [text ]<h5>Drop us a line</h5>[/text][contact_form to="support@plusquare.pt" title="Email from one of my site''s user" labels_pos="top" success="Message sent! Thanks for contacting us!" error="One or more fields are invalid!" ][contact_field type="name" required="true" ]Name[/contact_field][contact_field type="email" required="true" ]E-mail[/contact_field][contact_field type="textarea" required="true" ]Message[/contact_field][button text=''submit'']{"field0":"12","field1":"6","field2":"1","field3":"3","field4":"#ffffff","field5":"#ffffff","field6":"#776b5f","field7":"#e96b45","field8":"0","field9":"0","field10":"Open_Sans:300","field11":"13","field12":"#776b5f","field13":"#e96b45","field14":"0.1","field15":"ease-out","field16":"[i]fa-envelope-o[/i]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SEND","field17":"center"}[/button][/contact_form][vertical_space ]10[/vertical_space][/column][/row]', 'Standard Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '296-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-01 23:16:27', '2013-11-01 23:16:27', '', 296, 'replace_with_url296-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
