(948, 1, '2013-11-06 11:17:53', '2013-11-06 11:17:53', '[row snaps="000b"][column size="4" offset="4" content_align="center" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text_header font="Open_Sans:300" font_size="40" line_height="42" letterspacing="0.5" color="#e96b45" align="center" padding="20px 20px" border_width="0" border_style="solid" border_color="#ffffff" line_type="bottom" line_size="1" line_color="#e1e1e1" line_width="80" line_ver="-5" line_hor="0" ]Essenza V2 features[/text_header][vertical_space ]10[/vertical_space][/column][/row][row snaps="0000"][column size="9" offset="1" content_align="center" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text ]<p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Open Sans''; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px;">The reason that we created this demo is to show you what other possibilities Essenza has besides the default grid, gallery and blog modules.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Open Sans''; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px;">Essenza really is a premium theme with additional fullscreen grid and gallery options, instead of a grid based theme with some simple page options!&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Open Sans''; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px;">Based on all the feedback and suggestions we got during the first two weeks online, we decided to drastically change the &#39;regular&#39; page admin options, giving full freedom for creativity to the user!</span></p>[/text][/column][/row][row snaps="0lr0"][column size="12" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [quote author="" ]Essenza V2 is all about giving creative freedom to the user[/quote][/column][/row][row snaps="0000"][column size="4" offset="0" content_align="left" use_paddings="false" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"] [text_header font="Open_Sans:700" font_size="20" line_height="24" letterspacing="0" color="#444444" align="left" padding="20px 0px"